          "id": "msg_it_1_2",
          "from": "it-support@company.com",
          "to": [
            "sam.williams@company.com"
          ],
          "subject": "Re: Laptop fan running loudly and overheating (Ticket IT-3928)",
          "body": "Hi Sam,\n\nThanks for the additional detail.\n\nAs noted in the ticket, can you please:\n1) Install the latest macOS security update, and\n2) Send us a screenshot of Activity Monitor (sorted by CPU) when the fan is loud?\n\nYou can reply to this email with the screenshot attached and we’ll update the ticket on our side.\n\nBest,\nIT Support",
          "date": "2025-02-20T15:36:12-05:00"
        },
        {
          "id": "msg_it_1_3",
          "from": "sam.williams@company.com",
          "to": [
            "it-support@company.com"
          ],
          "subject": "Re: Laptop fan running loudly and overheating (Ticket IT-3928)",
